sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 👤 User
    participant Web as Next.js Frontend
    participant API as FastAPI Backend
    participant Storage as Supabase Storage (private)
    participant DB as Supabase PostgreSQL

    Note over User,DB: UPLOAD FLOW
    User->>Web: Select file in upload dialog
    Web->>API: POST multipart/form-data
    API->>API: Validate JWT + RBAC + ABAC
    API->>API: Validate filename / MIME type / size
    API->>Storage: Upload private immutable object
    API->>DB: INSERT document + document_version
    API->>DB: Store SHA-256 checksum + storage key
    API->>DB: Write audit event
    API-->>Web: DocumentResponse

    Note over User,DB: DOWNLOAD FLOW
    User->>Web: Click download
    Web->>API: GET /v1/document-versions/{id}/download-url
    API->>API: Authorization check
    API->>Storage: Generate short-lived signed URL
    API-->>Web: Signed URL
    Web->>Storage: Browser downloads directly
